Class AttributeCollectorVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.parse.visitor.OXPathVisitorGenericAdaptor<AttributeCollectorVisitor.MyData,CustomSimpleNode>
      • uk.ac.ox.cs.diadem.oxpath.utils.AttributeCollectorVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OXPathParserVisitor

    public class AttributeCollectorVisitor
extends OXPathVisitorGenericAdaptor<AttributeCollectorVisitor.MyData,CustomSimpleNode>
    Simple visitor implementation to print out OXPath expressions into String objects that are encoded as AST trees.
    Author:
    Giovanni Grasso
